## User Story

As a **user**, I want the **application UI to be mobile-friendly**, so that I can easily use it on my mobile device.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: The UI should resize and rearrange for smaller screens.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: Buttons should be large enough to click on mobile devices.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Use media queries to make the UI responsive.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Test on different mobile screen sizes.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: Low
- **Related Issues**: #105
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Focus on the most commonly used mobile resolutions.
